did.unittitle: Yale student papers collection

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The collection consists of research papers and essays by Yale students. Included are many prize-winning essays.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 47 (YRG 47), Collections documenting teaching and learning in Yale academic programs.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Copyright has not been transferred to Yale University. Written permission of the author is required for photocopying.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Yale Student Papers Collection (RU 331). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

relatedmaterial.head: Associated Materials
relatedmaterial.p: Related material: Senior Prize Essays from the Department of History, Yale University (RU 170), (Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.)

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The materials are arranged by accession.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The collection consists of research papers and essays by Yale students. Included are many prize-winning essays.
